fields.description:
• Conference takes place on Saturday, 3rd of October, in Zagreb.
  • Talks are either 25 or 45 minutes, including 5 minutes for Q&A.
  • Prior experience is not a prerequisite, we welcome first timers.
  • Talks must be in English.
  • Multiple talk submissions are welcome.

Our speaker package includes:

  • Full conference pass
  • 2 complimentary hotel nights for speakers remote to the area
  • Lunch and other activities included in the regular conference
  • Speakers dinner on October 2nd
  • A goodie bag with a speaker's T-shirt and other swag
fields.title: CFP 2015
